subject: File posted. Weird one.
author: lisbyfarrum
full_text:
Gimme some opinions on this one, gang. The first part of the clip is
the speed it can through at. The repeat is slowed by about 70 percent.
I hear it as "Estep." I thought I had heard the word yes, so I ask,
"Yes?" Under my voice is the name "Andrew," then "I'm Stu." "Perfect."
"No..??...asshole...fucking scared."

Do you hear this as I do? I'm postulating right now that because I
live immediately across the street from a cemetery, and in a
100-year-old sitting atop a 200+-year-old foundation and cellar, that
perhaps local dead folk who haven't crossed are popping in during
sessions. The voice that said "fucking scared" I swear I heard in
another file in my folder saying "scared people."

Ann
